│    if (*Offset > std::numeric_limits<int64_t>::max() - Size)                │
│      return std::nullopt;                                                   │
│    ```                                                                      │
│                                                                             │
│ This prevents invalid `ConstantRange` objects that cause the assertion      │
│ failure in `ConstantRangeList::insert`.                                     │
